list.name: Default
list.comment: Added GuiWindow and GuiText as GuiObject Subclasses. See LevelEdit project for implementation. This commit marks the merging of LevelEdit and FirstPyGame projects into one repo. I will be deleting the LevelEdit repo and will be committing changes to both projects through FirstPyGame. They work on the same code base and this makes more sense organizationally.
